# Hardened Arch Linux Templates for Railway - Git Ignore
#
# This file prevents sensitive data, personal configurations, and build artifacts
# from being committed to version control.
#
# IMPORTANT: Never commit:
#   - SSH keys or certificates
#   - API keys or tokens
#   - Environment files with secrets
#   - Personal deployment notes (PERSONAL.md)
#
# Safe to commit:
#   - .env.example (template files without real secrets)
#   - Documentation (*.md except PERSONAL.md)
#   - Source code and Dockerfiles
#   - Railway configuration (railway.toml)

# Personal deployment notes (contains SSH keys and sensitive data)
PERSONAL.md
PERSONAL_*.md
notes.md
